Text: Plan Locationsis the list that Steve mentioned in the staff meeting this morning Please review and let me know of any concerns Ray Forwarded by Ray StellyETSEnron on AM Steve Gilbert AM To Jo WilliamsET NRON Lindy DonohoET NRON cc Ray StellyET NRON John FiscusET NRON David ClementsET NRON Mike ZabawaET NRON Steven HarrisET NRON Dave NeubauerET NRON Subject Plan Locations At the Capital Officer review meeting Marketing agreed to review the Operations Capital Budget in order to confirm that the expenditures were consistent with the Business Plan ie from a Marketing perspective are we spending our capital dollars where we anticipate doing transactions In order to help this process attached is the Plan with locations identified Please review this list for any inconsistencies and inform Dave Clements of any concerns If at all possible provide your comments by close of business Tuesday August nd Thank you Forwarded by Steve GilbertETSEnron on AM From Mike Zabawa PM To Steve GilbertET NRON cc David ClementsET NRON Diane GottoET NRON Subject Plan Locations Let me try this again Forwarded by Mike ZabawaETSEnron on PM From Mike Zabawa PM To Steve GilbertET NRON cc David ClementsET NRON Diane GottoET NRON Subject Plan Locations Steve Attached is the spreadsheet that lists the location etc of the Operations group projects for the plan Please let us know when you would like to get together to discuss Mike
